          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1634721214492-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>to the pan and cook for 25-30 min, stirring frequently, or until the rice is cooked with a slight bite – this is your <strong>mushroom risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Add in the liquid all at once for ease, but don't forget to stir to release the starches in the rice!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1634721221773-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1634721221773-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1634721221773-x700.jpg",
